-765955505.text: Real-time PCR analysis indicated that knockdown of plexin-A1 decreased the basal levels of plexin-A1 and VEGFR2 expression and inhibited isoprenaline induced up-regulation of both plexin-A1 and VEGFR2 at mRNA levels.
